    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered its whole life, kept in a garage, and it drives like an absolute dream. No scratches, no spills, just pure perfection. I'm more than happy to chat or let you take a look whenever you're free so you can see for yourself. You seriously won't find one cleaner than this!",
