    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a peerless 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2) finished in concours-level condition. This specimen features the 3.6L flat-six M96 engine, fully documented with a dual-row IMS bearing retrofit and a recent RMS replacement. The 6-speed G96 manual gearbox delivers precise gate entry, paired with a factory-spec M030 sport suspension for sharpened turn-in and lateral stability. The chassis is free of oxidation, and the original paint retains full depth with no discernible swirl marks. This is a mechanically sorted, collector-grade vehicle with a comprehensive service dossier, catering to the most demanding purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
