    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that redefines the term 'mint condition.' This one-owner gem has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior finish is flawless, boasting its original deep luster with a professional ceramic coating applied to protect the paint from the elements; you will find no rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks here. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state, retaining that distinct new-car aroma. The premium leather upholstery shows absolutely no bolster wear, and the dashboard is free of any UV fading or imperfections. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It comes with a binder of every service receipt, documenting a proactive maintenance schedule that far exceeds factory recommendations. The engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, and the undercarriage remains factory-fresh. All electronics, safety features, and climate controls function perfectly. Equipped with nearly new high-performance tires and recently flushed fluids, this vehicle needs nothing but a new home. This is a rare opportunity to own a piece of automotive perfection that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line.",
      "price": 48900.0,
