      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, this car is in such incredible shape, it still feels like it just rolled off the lot! It\u2019s been pampered since day one\u2014always garaged and kept spotless. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the showroom price tag, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
