      "description": "Offered is a pristine example of the E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six powerplant. This high-revving unit utilizes individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing to deliver linear power up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential lock. The chassis remains structurally sound with no subframe fatigue, riding on staggered 19-inch forged wheels. Every mechanical component, from the rod bearings to the cooling system, has been maintained to an exacting standard. The exterior retains its factory deep-gloss finish, while the interior leather shows zero bolster wear, making this a true collector-grade specimen.",
